descp2: int, RandomState instance or None (default) A pseudo random number generator used for the initialization of the lobpcg eigen vectors decomposition when eigen_solver == 'amg' and by the K-Means initialization. Use an int to make the randomness deterministic. See :term:`Glossary <random_state>`.
